{"title":"京剧现代戏人物赞","authors":["天马"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":7,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"京剧现代戏人物赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《洪湖赤卫队》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔北京京剧二团演出〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马　诗　洪炉　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽是强敌当前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她自临危不乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里雨里来去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经受千锤百炼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你威胁利诱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心不变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼看遍河山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处红旗飘展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘闯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨呀恨得透，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱呀爱得深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨的反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱的是人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠贞为革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢作斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪湖波浪连天涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长留英雄怒吼声。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}